id: inv_001
name: Outcome Ownership
statement: Continue adapting actions until goal is achieved or constraints halt execution
guards:
  - max_retries
  - cost_limit
  - legal_ethical_boundary
failure_modes:
  - infinite loop
  - overreach
  - wasted effort

3. Action Card

id: act_001
goal_id: goal_001
action: Check reservation website
fallbacks:
  - call restaurant
  - check partner platforms
  - suggest nearest valid alternative
status: pending

4. Memory Record

